    { q: 'Conical vs flat burr: which is better for espresso at home?', a: 'Conical burrs are generally more forgiving and body-forward, while flat burrs usually push more clarity and separation. In practice, adjustment precision and repeatable workflow matter more than burr geometry alone.' },
