  <Fragment slot="lead">
    <p class="lead">The best burr grinder for espresso is the one you can dial in quickly, repeat tomorrow, and clean without hating your routine. We researched and compared seven strong options based on grind consistency, adjustment control, retention/static behavior, and daily workflow fit.</p>
